edu.udel.cis.taschd.extract

Class CAScheduleExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.taschd.extract.CAScheduleExtractor

  • public class CAScheduleExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    The CAScheduleExtractor class is responsible for extraction of details like CA Schedule, in a specific semester, CAID and CourseInstance/Section details are returned. It hides the details of extraction and assigns extracted values to CourseAssistant and CourseInstance objects. It also uses WeeklySchedule class variables.
